Package org.wso2.carbon.identity.discovery.builders

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OIDCProviderRequestBuilder
    OIDCProviderRequestBuilder should be implemented to build the OIDProviderRequest which should be used in the OIDC discovery context, using the HttpServletRequest and tenant.
    OIDProviderResponseBuilder
    OIDProviderResponseBuilder should be implemented to get the required format which represents the information in OIDProviderConfigResponse instance
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultOIDCProviderRequestBuilder
    DefaultOIDCProviderRequestBuilder is the default OIDCProviderRequestBuilder provided in the discovery module.
    ProviderConfigBuilder
    ProviderConfigBuilder builds the OIDProviderConfigResponse giving the correct OprnIDConnect settings.
